channel.title: Drywall2
channel.description: A RSS dedicated to companion news.

item.title: Destiny Couples Selfie
item.dc:creator: Rgocal
item.description: Despite the hate this game gets, Destiny 2 is my favorite game to play with family and friends. Especially this lucky lady!

item.title: Droid 4
item.dc:creator: Rgocal
item.description: One of the most popular wallpapers to be downloaded in my Bionx Roms, This wallpaper excerted alot of power and emotion to the Droid Community. Something I miss about Motorola is the whole mech theme of android.

item.title: Bionx Chasm
item.dc:creator: Rgocal
item.description: The main wallpaper of Bionx Nx, The Droid Chasm was an edited version of the Droid Chasm from the Droid 3 or 2 I believe. I had a strong passion for the Droid series.

item.title: Bionx
item.dc:creator: Rgocal
item.description: The main wallpaper in Bionx for the LG Ally. Bionx was my very first custom rom back in the last quarter of 2010 and this wallpaper excerted an amount of energy. The very same evergy fueled the community that backed my development and created who I am today.

item.title: Holo Floral
item.dc:creator: Unknown
item.description: I don't remember much of where this wallpaper came from except for the fact it came from an early distributuion of MIUI when I tried building the rom for the LG Ally and Droid Razr.

item.title: Catalyst
item.dc:creator: Unknown
item.description: The main wallpaper for Bionx Nx Catalyst. Catalyst became known as the greatest stock custom rom for the Droid Razr. It was infused with the Sony Xperia Z firmware for a high quality media rom and very beautiful in style.

item.title: Presence
item.dc:creator: Lance Palmer
item.description: The pure nature of this photo is just amazing. That is all.

item.title: Xperia X
item.dc:creator: Sony
item.description: The beginning of a new series of devices. This was one of my favorites!

item.title: Null Galaxy
item.dc:creator: Samsung
item.description: I beleive this was apart of the wallpaper collection for the release of the Galaxy S6. Im a big fan of the art style ol Sam has used for the Samsung Galaxy wallpapers.

item.title: Marble
item.dc:creator: Unknown
item.description: This is a marble...and it is very shiny indeed. Truthfully, I just needed that 10th photo in this collection...Harder than I thought?
